SpoonerPlacements.Note: Like any proud citizen of Los Santos, you've seen the shopping carts, dead bodies and rusted pickups filling the Land Act Reservoir, and you think it's a disgrace. This city deserves a better class of refuse in its main water supply, and a few crashed muscle cars, vintage motorbikes and stunt planes would go a long way to raising those standards. Time to show you care. Lap Transform Race starting with the Ruiner 2000, also featuring motorcycles, Havok, Blazer Aqua and Mallard.
